Purpose & context
Jose is building HIIT-Gym, a full-stack gym website hosted on Cloudflare Pages with 
Supabase for authentication and database. The project includes pages for class types (modalidades), 
user profiles, and coach information. The stack uses vanilla JS, CSS with nesting, 
and Supabase for auth and enrollment data, allong with vscode->github->cloudflare.

